fields.name: Skzoo memo pad Wolf Chan (Bangchan)
fields.description: Consist of 30 pages. Pages are not sticky like post-it notes, so make a fun area to scribble down phone messages, post a reminder on the fridge, slip a note into someone's lunch, use on the desk as a reminder pad, or even as a bookmark or page marker. Depending on each person's screen settings, colours may vary somewhat. There will be no refunds for small colour variations. This like all the other notepads on my shop has a hard backing so you can use it everywhere. Width: 10.cm Height: 10cm
